title: Ep. 44 :: Conservative Option Strategies
itunes:title: Conservative Option Strategies
description: Lee Lowell, option specialist and editor of The Instant Money Trader, talks about selling puts on America's favorite large-cap companies. David Eifrig, ex-Goldman trader and editor of S&A's Retirement Trader, educates us on LEAPS and covered calls.
